# OrderFlow — Todo el tráfico pasa por el Gateway
@api = https://localhost:8080

### ─── 1. LOGIN — Customer ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{api}}/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email":    "john@techshop.es",
  "password": "Customer1234!"
}
### → { "access_token": "eyJ...", "token_type": "Bearer", "expires_in": 3600 }

@token = PEGAR_TOKEN_AQUI

### ─── 2. PEDIDO CON TOKEN ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{api}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "john@techshop.es",
  "items": [{
    "productId":   "REEMPLAZAR_CON_ID_REAL",
    "productName": "MacBook Pro 16\" M4",
    "quantity": 1,
    "unitPrice":   3999.99,
    "currency":    "EUR"
  }],
  "shippingAddress": {
    "street":  "Gran Vía 28",
    "city":    "Madrid",
    "zipCode": "28013",
    "country": "ES"
  }
}
### → 201 Created — customerId se toma del JWT (sub), no del body

### ─── 3. LISTAR PEDIDOS (solo los del customer autenticado) ─────────────────
GET {{api}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### → 200 OK con los pedidos del customer

### ─── 4. SIN TOKEN — debe devolver 401 ──────────────────────────────────────
GET {{api}}/api/orders
### → 401 Unauthorized

### ─── 5. LOGIN ADMIN ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{api}}/account/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@techshop.es", "password": "Admin1234!" }

@adminToken = PEGAR_TOKEN_ADMIN_AQUI

### ─── 6. CONFIRMAR PEDIDO (solo admin) ──────────────────────────────────────
### Con token customer → 403 Forbidden
### Con token admin    → 204 No Content
POST {{api}}/api/orders/REEMPLAZAR_CON_ID_REAL/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── HEALTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{api}}/health
### → {"status":"Healthy"}

### ─── PRODUCTOS (sin autenticación) ─────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{api}}/api/products
### → YARP enruta a products-api/api/products
